VenderInfo.Name: Cypress
VenderInfo.Description: EZ-PD Configuration Utility is a GUI based Microsoft Windows application developed by Cypress to guide a CCGx user through the process of configuring and programming the chip. The utility allows users to: 1. Select and configure the parameters they want to modify 2. Program the resulting configuration onto the target CCGx device.
